Package: ptvapi
Title: A Wrapper for the Public Transport Victoria Timetable API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Neuzerling",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david@neuzerling.com")
Description: Access the Public Transport Victoria Timetable API, with results
    passed as familiar R data structures. Retrieve information on stops, routes,
    disruptions, departures, and more.
